Khyva St. Albans https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Khyva_St._Albans 0 Khyva St. Albans (1896-1989), also known as Zara Alexeyewa, Ayenara Alexeyeva, and Elinore Saenger, was an American actress, dancer, and choreographer. She was a longtime resident of Ajijic, on Lake Chapala in Mexico.
